<treatmentCitationGroup id="E3DC11F5FFD0166B20E6EBEDFD47FE6E" box="[178,697,478,500]" pageId="18" pageNumber="209">
<treatmentCitation id="426D10CAFFD0166B20E6EBEDFDDCFE6E" author="ASSING V" box="[178,546,478,500]" httpUri="http://treatment.plazi.org/id/C92CAF45FF5E4B351A7330AA1C97FD9A" page="62" pageId="18" pageNumber="209" year="2015">
<taxonomicName id="04CC4D58FFD0166B20E6EBEDFDDCFE6E" authority="ASSING, 2015: 62" authorityName="ASSING" authorityPageNumber="62" authorityYear="2015" box="[178,546,478,500]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="209" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="abruptum">
<emphasis id="F1B8EAC9FFD0166B20E6EBEDFE85FE69" box="[178,379,478,499]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="209">Lathrobium abruptum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="A75D4B2AFFD0166B21D5EBEDFDDCFE6E" author="ASSING V" box="[385,546,478,500]" pageId="18" pageNumber="209" pagination="41 - 74" refId="ref10138" refString="ASSING V. (2015): New species and additional records of Lathrobium and Elytrobium from the Palaearctic region, with special reference to the fauna of East Yunnan (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Contributions to Entomology 65 (1): 41 - 74." type="journal article" year="2015">ASSING, 2015: 62</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</treatmentCitation>
ff; preoccupied.
</treatmentCitationGroup>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C37336DBFFD0166B20E6E836FEBBFD15" blockId="18.[178,1085,517,656]" pageId="18" pageNumber="209">
C o m m e n t: 
<taxonomicName id="04CC4D58FFD0166B2108E836FD2DFD81" authority="ASSING, 2015" authorityName="ASSING" authorityYear="2015" box="[348,723,517,539]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="209" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="abruptum">
<emphasis id="F1B8EAC9FFD0166B2108E836FDC3FD80" box="[348,573,517,538]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="209">Lathrobium abruptum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="A75D4B2AFFD0166B2210E836FD2DFD81" author="ASSING V" box="[580,723,517,539]" pageId="18" pageNumber="209" pagination="41 - 74" refId="ref10138" refString="ASSING V. (2015): New species and additional records of Lathrobium and Elytrobium from the Palaearctic region, with special reference to the fauna of East Yunnan (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Contributions to Entomology 65 (1): 41 - 74." type="journal article" year="2015">ASSING, 2015</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, a name recently given to a species from the Gongga Shan in 
<collectingRegion id="0108F839FFD0166B21EAE811FDECFDA2" box="[446,530,546,568]" country="China" name="Sichuan" pageId="18" pageNumber="209">Sichuan</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="BBDB764BFFD0166B2249E811FDA2FDA2" box="[541,604,546,568]" name="China" pageId="18" pageNumber="209">China</collectingCountry>
, is preoccupied by 
<taxonomicName id="04CC4D58FFD0166B2370E810FBC7FDAD" authority="ASSING, 2014" authorityName="ASSING" authorityYear="2014" box="[804,1081,546,568]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="209" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="abruptum">
<emphasis id="F1B8EAC9FFD0166B2370E810FC5CFDAD" box="[804,930,546,568]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="209">L. abruptum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="A75D4B2AFFD0166B23FEE811FBC7FDAD" author="ASSING V" box="[938,1081,546,567]" pageId="18" pageNumber="209" pagination="1 - 28" refId="ref10096" refString="ASSING V. (2014): New species and records of Lathrobium from the Palaearctic region, primarily from Nepal (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Contributions to Entomology 64 (1): 1 - 28." type="journal article" year="2014">ASSING, 2014</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, the name of a species from West 
<collectingCountry id="BBDB764BFFD0166B2244E80CFDAEFDCF" box="[528,592,575,597]" name="Nepal" pageId="18" pageNumber="209">Nepal</collectingCountry>
. The junior homonym is here replaced with the nomen novum 
<taxonomicName id="04CC4D58FFD0166B211EE86EFE12FDEB" authorityName="Assing" authorityYear="2016" box="[330,492,604,626]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Lathrobium" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="209" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="novabruptum">
<emphasis id="F1B8EAC9FFD0166B211EE86EFE12FDEB" box="[330,492,604,626]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="209">L. novabruptum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, a combination of the Latin adjective novus (new) and the original name.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
